            <h1 class="entry-title post__header__title">【花絮】“模擬社會人”2019年澳門學生實習計劃</h1>
            <div class="post__header__events"><!-- <time class="updated" datetime="2019-04-10T09:55:15+00:00">2019-04-10</time> -->
<ul class="simple">
    	    		    		<li data-link="【花絮】學聯模擬社會人計劃，體驗職場人生">
    			<!-- <a href="https://aecm.org.mo/%e3%80%90%e6%8e%a8%e4%bb%8b%e3%80%91%e6%a8%a1%e6%93%ac%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e4%ba%ba2019%e5%b9%b4%e6%be%b3%e9%96%80%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e5%af%a6%e7%bf%92%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83-%e5%8d%97/#【花絮】學聯模擬社會人計劃，體驗職場人生"><span>-</span> 【花絮】學聯模擬社會人計劃，體驗職場人生</a> -->
          <a href="https://aecm.org.mo/%e3%80%90%e6%8e%a8%e4%bb%8b%e3%80%91%e6%a8%a1%e6%93%ac%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e4%ba%ba2019%e5%b9%b4%e6%be%b3%e9%96%80%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e5%af%a6%e7%bf%92%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83-%e5%8d%97/#collapse1"><span>-</span> 【花絮】學聯模擬社會人計劃，體驗職場人生</a>
				    				<i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-down"></i>
				    		</li>
